INSTALLATION

1.
  Drop "Reporting" folder from this archive into in the "plugins"
  folder of your MantisBT installation. Please note that folder name is
  case-sensitive!

2.
  In your MantisBT's Web interface go to "Manage" -> "Manage Plugins"
  and click on "Install" for "Reporting" plugin.

Typical structure looks like this:

    << mantisbt >>
    | -- api
    | -- core
    | ...
    | ...
    | -- plugins
    |     | -- Reporting
    |     |     | -- files
    |     |     | -- lang
    |     |     | -- pages
    |     |     | -- INSTALL
    |     |     | -- Reporting.php



UPGRADE

1.
  Make backup of your local "Reporting_AdeRHis" folder and then remove it.
  Unpack content of the downloaded archive into the same place.

2.
  Check if database "upgrade" is needed on the "Manage Plugins" page.
  Check plugin configuration page to see if there are new settings or
  reports.



